左第2個師傅比我 上左唔夠5粒鐘去考 結果唔熟架車 死左火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c03915866cf10611bc24e72843e008343dc8ab","tid":124563,"uid":9610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"留返啲錢搭的士好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3feffc0c9373932ef493f8af1f05b9d3d0cc75cb","tid":124563,"uid":81066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:04:49.000Z","msg":"無人島無以前咁好考, 以前好似個遊樂場咁圍住個圈走, 家個入口同出口都好窄...<br />\n而且果度D車多少真係好難以預計, 有時塞到HIHI上唔倒3波, 有時條路又好順,有時又有D狗走出黎..<br />\n睇你臨場既運數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我補考果次連上3日補7堂, 個新場個入口我係考果日先一次入, 因之前整路, 其實我原先都預壽味, 但最尾我極力子踩BRAKE用一個極慢極慢既速度入去, 順利過關, 好多野都係考果日之前果幾個鐘吸返黎, 例如上果條假斜路唔好踏BRAKE極力子要高唔係會留後, 出個試場果要扭番圈右之後出哂先回左, 險過銻頭......總言之想PASS考時唔好急順其自然, 安全第一唔死火一定PASS"},{"pid":"be03cf296aedfc0b0203d66a42c2ab7dea2eaf01","tid":124563,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>始終都係睇個人<br />\n我駕院考兩次自動波都肥<br />\n利申：放棄左</blockquote><br />\n放棄就岩喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36570344cbcd8c4e5ad54930c018c4a1f224913","tid":124563,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"技術、判斷力唔夠可以補鐘練番嚟<br />\n但要諗下之前錯乜而對症下藥，同埋改善心理質素、駕駛態度"},{"pid":"7d9eef7889de6731f6aae9ff3f891df6c6090cbf","tid":124563,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人島無以前咁好考, 以前好似個遊樂場咁圍住個圈走, 家個入口同出口都好窄...<br />\n而且果度D車多少真係好難以預計, 有時塞到HIHI上唔倒3波, 有時條路又好順,有時又有D狗走出黎..<br />\n睇你臨場既運數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我補考果次連上3日補7堂, 個新場個入口我係考果日先一次入, 因之前整路, 其實我原先都預壽味, 但最尾我極力子踩BRAKE用一個極慢極慢既速度入去, 順利過關, 好多野都係考果日之前果幾個鐘吸返黎, 例如上果條假斜路唔好踏BRAKE極力子要高唔係會留後, 出個試場果要扭番圈右之後出哂先回左, 險過銻頭......總言之想PASS考時唔好急順其自然, 安全第一唔死火一定PASS</blockquote><br />\n吓姐係依家唔係圍圈咁考？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6094f5119917e2d7fc3e3f6edcbfc37b112ae1c1","tid":124563,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>技術、判斷力唔夠可以補鐘練番嚟<br />\n但要諗下之前錯乜而對症下藥，同埋改善心理質素、駕駛態度</blockquote><br />\n點樣可以冇咁緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a3b04206e07d1bb30b5804e623e7ed42526cd9","tid":124563,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:41:33.000Z","msg":"一樣，之後唔撚考"},{"pid":"5644416df6ede0a5f2788d11f2bdcbbb8eb20bac","tid":124563,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>始終都係睇個人<br />\n我駕院考兩次自動波都肥<br />\n利申：放棄左</blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"c1e0b7099f17f58f913d492a06b22f37435c3766","tid":124563,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣，之後唔撚考</blockquote><br />\n為左我夢想 冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e2495375d0e28c3fb340b9a7df3fdd9c68b41a","tid":124563,"uid":69098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一樣，之後唔撚考</blockquote><br />\n為左我夢想 冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n為咗香港路人既安全&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf64d506b2d720bd0db858e487ba0fcbb523836d","tid":124563,"uid":33826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T18:48:03.000Z","msg":"唔好以為駕院就一定易同必定合格先得嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢果啲合格率我當初個師傳話咪鬼信，合唔合到格根本睇你個人<br />\n<br />\n駕院優勢基本上係個乙部，路試都係睇你做化，你話街多死車駕院啲線都一樣多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大把人連過死車啲步驟都做唔足直接肥左，俾啲仆街司機同行人害都會有唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，考唔掂真係寧願樓主搭的士好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecc11c78b97b0608dd1ae0f63378bd30df8fe4a","tid":124563,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T19:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好以為駕院就一定易同必定合格先得嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢果啲合格率我當初個師傳話咪鬼信，合唔合到格根本睇你個人<br />\n<br />\n駕院優勢基本上係個乙部，路試都係睇你做化，你話街多死車駕院啲線都一樣多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大把人連過死車啲步驟都做唔足直接肥左，俾啲仆街司機同行人害都會有唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，考唔掂真係寧願樓主搭的士好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但鴨駕起碼冇大球場咁多車多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f05c9d360a26a6b939bd1a5b1af3f240792c01","tid":124563,"uid":27537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T19:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我考第3次先pass <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係掃桿埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我重考都要成3400蚊一次</blockquote><br />\n認得你啦巴打 我第2次衰唔熟架車 果日個師傅咁岩唔得閒 撞正冬至 佢安排左第2個師傅比我 上左唔夠5粒鐘去考 結果唔熟架車 死左火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你著番對薄底鞋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我著對stansmith 考之後就得左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係補6個鐘，最緊要考之前操番陣，最好開車之前好似考26d人咁，扮下野望左右加下分先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 周不時就睇下鏡扮下野，如果你係考斜佬去到黃泥涌道記得cut右，因為超多死車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去到禮頓山先cut左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac1bd5fa148b6d8a547aa9213ce6827b30513ba","tid":124563,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:28:47.000Z","msg":"試下駕院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4939bb904853603917d7a2142c4d02f00f2a83d","tid":124563,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a586e4295208ceec0bdd371d07d37b433cd41d21","tid":124563,"uid":21064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"1次就話唔好彩<br />\n2次既話有無諗過係個人問題"},{"pid":"c6066fd5d7df192539760031770d16dd04101de9","tid":124563,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下駕院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但上面有人話駕院都唔係咁易 都唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a004815c64fd12e976da164a2ef30226b325b142","tid":124563,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1次就話唔好彩<br />\n2次既話有無諗過係個人問題</blockquote><br />\n第二次我諗係唔熟架車 因為架車好新 落左地冇耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c2def8d2c7d73746be0dbeea3fd9e620671c80","tid":124563,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:06:56.000Z","msg":"之前睇過<br />\n駕院既合格率都係5成左右（街師傅4成）<br />\n點解成日講到駕院實pass咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7176606aa94309f62c75adeb5e51eb8ec18c94be","tid":124563,"uid":30991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦，無謂揸架車出黎害死人</blockquote><br />\n肥左兩次 最後放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdae7d05192638b31471d98849a7b9878e2c3fd","tid":124563,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"大球場 你抽到九點到十一點呢d時間咪無乜人同車囉<br />\n利申：兩次都係朝早"},{"pid":"4fa4a86e5023a60979937f6d13eca234d9de202d","tid":124563,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T03:45:29.000Z","msg":"咁多人肥2次就放棄  識一條友又係"},{"pid":"bfc079918f5b64c98a04b38aa945d725db64d07f","